descriptionHtml:
Treasure Hunt MOD


There are 10 Hidden Super Treasures absolutely HARD to find.

all around Skyrim and Solstheim.


This are the only clues:

10 Treasures:
    7 Skyrim
        2 Lakes and Rivers
        3 Land/Mountains
        2 Ocean

    3 Solstheim
        2 Ocean
        1 Land/Mountains
        


Every Chest, do not Respawn, every one have a unique item
added by this mod and a lot of treasure and gold.


HAPPY ADVENTURE!


List of Objects:
-----------------
Golden Shell
Golden Star
Golden Lamp
Golden Apple
Telescope
Guitar
Corven Lute
Gramophone
Harp
Lyre
